==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Denotate
<hw>De*no"tate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>denotatus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>denotare</ets>.]</ety> <def>To mark
off; to denote.</def> <mark>[Archaic]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>These terms <qex>denotate</qex> a longer time.</q>
<rj><qau>Burton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>What things should be <qex>denotated</qex> and signified by the
color.</q> <rj><qau>Urquhart.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Denotation</ent>⟦br⟧
